**Headline finding:** the sotorasib PFS benefit is concentrated entirely in `kras_g12c=1 AND sex_female=0` (+4.64 months, pâ‰ˆ0); KRAS+ females and KRAS- patients show no benefit. The other three targeted therapies (pembrolizumab, olaparib, osimertinib) are null even within their canonical biomarker subgroups (PD-L1â‰¥0.5, BRCA2+, EGFR+).
